cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and text summarization. It may also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a neural network model for generating abstractive summaries. Additionally, it may be relevant to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it involves selecting important information from input text and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it uses a neural network for the proposed model.
